  <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
  <p class="updated">Last updated: March 26, 2026</p>

  <p>WhatsApp Chat Widget ("the App") is built to help Shopify merchants connect with their customers via WhatsApp. This Privacy Policy explains what data we collect, why we collect it, and how we use it.</p>

  <h2>1. Data We Collect</h2>
  <p>When a merchant installs the App, we collect and store:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>The store domain name (e.g., yourstore.myshopify.com)</li>
    <li>A Shopify access token to interact with the store API on your behalf</li>
    <li>Widget configuration settings (WhatsApp number, button text, placement options)</li>
    <li>Anonymized click event data (page URL, placement type, timestamp)</li>
  </ul>
  <p>We do <strong>not</strong> collect or store any personal information belonging to a store's customers (e.g., names, emails, phone numbers, order details).</p>

  <h2>2. How We Use Your Data</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>To render your WhatsApp widget on your storefront</li>
    <li>To provide click analytics within your admin dashboard</li>
    <li>To manage your subscription and billing through the Shopify Billing API</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>3. Data Sharing</h2>
  <p>We do not sell, rent, or share your data with any third parties. Data is stored securely in our database (hosted on Railway) and is only accessible to the App.</p>

  <h2>4. Data Retention</h2>
  <p>When you uninstall the App, your store's access token is immediately revoked. Your configuration data and analytics are retained for 30 days after uninstall before being permanently deleted.</p>

  <h2>5. GDPR Compliance</h2>
  <p>We respond to all mandatory Shopify GDPR webhooks, including customer data requests and erasure requests. If you are a merchant or a customer with a data request, please contact us at the email below.</p>

  <h2>6. Security</h2>
  <p>All data is transmitted over HTTPS (TLS 1.2+) and stored in an encrypted database. Access tokens are never logged or exposed.</p>

  <h2>7. Contact</h2>
  <p>If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at: <a href="mailto:support@rivertonmarkets.com">support@rivertonmarkets.com</a></p>

  <footer>© 2026 WhatsApp Chat Widget. All rights reserved.</footer>
